products.description:
Jeans with a slim fit are narrowed models that allow you to move freely and do not cause discomfort while walking.

Material:
- premium quality European denim fabric;
- 100% cotton.

Details and cut:
- slim fit;
- fastener in the form of buttons;
- two pockets in the front and two in the back;
- the belt fastens with a button, there are loops for the belt (the width of the loops is 5 cm);
- a tag with the Staff logo is sewn on the back.

Season:
- year-round

Color:
- shabby blue.

Care:
- washing in normal mode at a temperature not higher than 30°C, without spinning;
- bleaching is prohibited;
- dry in a suspended state, without using artificial drying.

On the picture:
- height of the model - 175 cm;
- model weight - 71 kg;
- size of things - "31".

